{"tid":734884,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不小心就證明了 LIVE 實力！BTOB 星材在《人氣歌謠》意外笑場","createTime":"2018-07-09T04:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T14:32:51.000Z","uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2329d684ead8b2c455886fb6fc425594b42f5b53","tid":734884,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"除了怕蟲出名的恩光，還有什麼會為 BTOB 的現場表演帶來「驚喜」呢？各種可能的答案恐怕連他們自己都難以預測吧！<br />\n<br />\n今天（8 日）在 SBS 播出的《人氣歌謠》中，BTOB 全員大展牛仔褲時尚，為這三週的打歌活動劃下清涼句點。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道不按牌理出牌的 BTOB 就算是表演同一首歌，每次都可能出現意料之外的驚喜，而今天的主角就是老么星材啦！<br />\n<br />\n第一次副歌結束後進入他的 solo，每次這段和舞者的甜蜜互動都掀起不少尖叫。沒想到從背後靠近時一個碰撞，舞者差點沒站穩，和星材兩人忍不住立刻笑場 XD<br />\n<br />\n不過星材歌聲裡的那絲笑意，也再次證明了 BTOB 總是現場演唱的實力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2018-07-08/107215-632168.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2018-07-08%2F107215-632168.png&h=4fc8faaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自：<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/107215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F107215&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e8b291fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/107215</a>"},{"pid":"4b0ae0c3737a9664ac7eec724274b27adcab279e","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"好少隊會喺人氣歌謠真唱<br />\n反而音中，音銀，冠軍秀會多啲"},{"pid":"cc9e4dc8c1572e23f0c866095c8969217b3cd42b","tid":734884,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b0ae0c3737a9664ac7eec724274b27adcab279e","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"好少隊會喺人氣歌謠真唱<br />\n反而音中，音銀，冠軍秀會多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"點分係咪真唱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317644780eb78862c222d32c37ff226141defc45","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s