2wVu1j78QzE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2wVu1j78QzE&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2ed9acfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2wVu1j78QzE</a><br />\n而依加音樂節目普遍得呢幾種<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/151214_92ce1acea72e187d62f06d47f2fd4614.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F151214_92ce1acea72e187d62f06d47f2fd4614.png&h=6592ac70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAR：有啲厚面皮嘅，直接播音源，另外錄都廢事，呢個最易認<br />\nLive AR:播之前錄定嘅音源（有呼吸聲），簡稱預錄，呢個要聽幾次唔同嘅節目去分辨，因為每次啲聲都係一樣。<br />\nLive MR:都係預錄，不過高音嗰度有墊音，或者輕鬆嘅part冇人聲<br />\nMR:只係播音樂，完全人聲<br />\nLive:連音樂都係即場演奏<br />\n不過有啲公司好蠱惑，就算live AR,都會開咪，啲藝人講幾句開唔開心，一齊尖叫，啲觀眾就以為唱live<br />\n仲有啲藝人明明咪緊咀都調整下咪，真係幾好戲。"},{"pid":"7de353b87613cda1f6ad0dcc18640891f5644046","tid":734884,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"635ac54b3cdebd91539ad24abdf7edadc0e21709","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"基本分辨呢條片有教<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2wVu1j78QzE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2wVu1j78QzE&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2ed9acfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2wVu1j78QzE</a><br />\n而依加音樂節目普遍得呢幾種<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/151214_92ce1acea72e187d62f06d47f2fd4614.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F151214_92ce1acea72e187d62f06d47f2fd4614.png&h=6592ac70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAR：有啲厚面皮嘅，直接播音源，另外錄都廢事，呢個最易認<br />\nLive AR:播之前錄定嘅音源（有呼吸聲），簡稱預錄，呢個要聽幾次唔同嘅節目去分辨，因為每次啲聲都係一樣。<br />\nLive MR:都係預錄，不過高音嗰度有墊音，或者輕鬆嘅part冇人聲<br />\nMR:只係播音樂，完全人聲<br />\nLive:連音樂都係即場演奏<br />\n不過有啲公司好蠱惑，就算live AR,都會開咪，啲藝人講幾句開唔開心，一齊尖叫，啲觀眾就以為唱live<br />\n仲有啲藝人明明咪緊咀都調整下咪，真係幾好戲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1aa9313ee11a6ff92eaa9bf97a800fd02506c3c","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"搞錯，打得咁辛苦你俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e757831c45680c73e15c563aec7df115158d83ed","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1QUPWO_2ILU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1QUPWO_2ILU&d=qeQ5DQznnouuRGWXlpqzrghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bb700570\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1QUPWO_2ILU</a><br />\n呢場就係Twice嘅Signal<br />\n流程表就寫明係Live AR開mic <br />\n明顯就係預錄大大聲播<br />\n自己細細聲唱咁<br />\n開咪係俾佢地打招呼用"},{"pid":"8ac91ce8d7efc889e8c1503f2cc354ce4bff741c","tid":734884,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1aa9313ee11a6ff92eaa9bf97a800fd02506c3c","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"搞錯，打得咁辛苦你俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"冇諗到聽首歌都咁複習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7882f9d77ffc9eb5af50135497549d1dc386762e","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac91ce8d7efc889e8c1503f2cc354ce4bff741c","tid":734884,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1aa9313ee11a6ff92eaa9bf97a800fd02506c3c","tid":734884,"uid":93046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"搞錯，打得咁辛苦你俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"冇諗到聽首